Configuring IPsec with ipsecctl(8)

Design guidelines

compact syntax based on pf
reasonable defaults
replaces both ipsecadm(8) and isakmpd.conf(5)
configures static IPsec with PFKEYv2 messages
configures isakmpd by entering commands into the FIFO UI

